thread.title: Janine Hannan
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Janine Hannan

author: Janine Hannan
title: Janine Hannan
text: I had to sell my brother and sister-in-laws flat in Hawthorn as they had to go into a care facility fairly quickly. I had only just finished moving all the contents out and called Nick Whyte to come and do an appraisal. He and his assistant Jessika Spink, were so professional and I felt comfortable in leaving all details up to them. They suggested slight renovations and got a stylist in to maximise the saleability, and boy did it work out beautifully. The price we got at auction was above and beyond our expectations. I am very pleased to recommend this company to anyone selling their home.
